{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a03d564b48","title":"诉衰情","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6a300ae43d","index":0,"year":1974,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"a03d564b48"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"fe116555c2","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东写给周恩来的一首词。当时，毛泽东身体不好，疾病缠身，周恩来惠有癌症，亦在重病中。这首词，字数虽不多，但周恩来为无产阶级共产主义事业奋斗一生的豪情，却跃然纸上。毛泽东已经预感到，革命将发生曲折，他和周恩来等老一辈无产阶级革命家凤愿将要“付与东流”。他问自己，也问周恩来：社会主义的红色江山究竟“靠谁守”？此词情感真挚，读来令人潜然泪下。酬，报答。为国酬，就是“为酬国”。14]已秋，两发白如同秋霜，喻年事已高。忍，艺忍。凤愿，平素的愿望。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e94541d837","type":"title","text":"诉袁情","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48"},{"id":"fe116555c2","type":"paragraph","text":"父母忠贞为国酬，何曾怕断头。如今天下红通，江山靠谁守？业未就，身驱倦，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48"},{"id":"3c80174c12","type":"subtitle","text":"已秋。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48"},{"id":"101d6e1d97","type":"paragraph","text":"你我之辈，忍叫将凤愿，付与东流？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48"}],"page":{"id":"4f3c5d2201","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"a03d564b48","start":532,"end":532}}}},"__N_SSG":true}